summary:
A fourth-year business student at Fontys University of Applied Sciences located in Venlo, the Netherlands. During the past two years, I gained lots of knowledge in the fields of marketing, finances, supply chain, and HR. I am also interested in learning new languages and at the moment I am studying Dutch and German. 

Regarding my most valuable skills, I am an extremely fast learner, team-oriented, can work under pressure and flexibility, and with a combination of my communication abilities, I am one very outstanding and valuable young person.

Future-wise, I am looking for all kinds of opportunities to develop myself and the skills I have and learn many more.
